      "anchor_id": "issue-gothrumedia-streeteditor-flutter-103",
      "display_title": "Issue #103: Handle Issue Endless Loading on WiFi Connection Step (Insta360 Camera)",
      "main_description_html": "<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"images/image-5f587acf-ae8e-4719-b79b-cba6f6539a8b.png\"><img width=\"329\" height=\"65\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"images/image-5f587acf-ae8e-4719-b79b-cba6f6539a8b.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 65px;; aspect-ratio: 329 / 65; background-color: var(--bgColor-muted); border-radius: 6px\" class=\"js-gh-image-fallback\"></a>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Description</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">A user reported a critical connection hang on the Android platform. When attempting to connect to the Insta360 camera, the Bluetooth connection establishes successfully, but the process gets permanently stuck on the \"connecting to wifi\" stage.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">The user attempted the connection twice, and both times it resulted in an endless loading state with no error messages or timeouts displayed.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Environment &amp; Details</p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Platform: Android</li>\n<li>Component: Camera WiFi Provisioning / Network State</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Acceptance Criteria</p>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>The Android app successfully transitions from Bluetooth pairing to a stable WiFi connection with the Insta360 camera.</li>\n<li>If the WiFi connection fails, the app does not hang indefinitely; it must time out and show a clear error message.</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">QA Tester Summary - Issue <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4764650182\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/streeteditor-flutter/issues/103\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/streeteditor-flutter/issues/103/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/streeteditor-flutter/issues/103\">#103</a>: Handle Issue Endless Loading on WiFi Connection Step (Insta360 Camera)</h3>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> 1. The Android app successfully transitions from Bluetooth pairing to a stable WiFi connection with the Insta360 camera.</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Xiaomi 13T</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>🐞[360 Camera Connection] Error 3208 appears when connecting to a 360 camera via Wi-Fi</em></p>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-6.5ZM11 8.825l3.5 2.1v-5.85l-3.5 2.1Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n    <span class=\"m-1\">WhatsApp.Video.2026-06-30.at.17.37.24.mp4</span>\n    <span class=\"dropdown-caret\"></span>\n  </summary>\n\n  <video src=\"videos/video-1ba75644-80c6-4349-9bf8-baa1d98f594d.mp4\" data-canonical-src=\"videos/video-1ba75644-80c6-4349-9bf8-baa1d98f594d.mp4\" controls=\"controls\" muted=\"muted\" class=\"d-block rounded-bottom-2 border-top width-fit\" style=\"max-height:640px; min-height: 200px\">\n\n  </video>\n</details>\n\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Completed task\" checked=\"\"> 2. If the WiFi connection fails, the app does not hang indefinitely; it must time out and show a clear error message.</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Samsung A23</strong></p>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-h